The paper deals with natural language generation, attention mechanisms, and deep learning models for negotiation in online shopping. Therefore, it is most likely to belong to the sub-category of Computation and Language (cs.CL). Additionally, the paper involves the use of artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), and machine learning (cs.LG) techniques. Finally, the paper also deals with information retrieval (cs.IR) as it involves extracting relevant information from multiple sources.
